rows.label: qst700108_msg0001
rows.name: Hey, it's you guys!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0002
rows.name:
Thank you so, so much!
The Armus are back safely,
and it's all thanks to you!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0003
rows.name: Mmmh... *sniffle, sniffle*

rows.label: qst700108_msg0004
rows.name: Oh, come on. Stop crying!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm... I'm not crying, you're crying!
You, you, you dolt...

rows.label: qst700108_msg0006
rows.name:
You're so nosy, you know that?
Stop sticking your nose in my
business!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0007
rows.name:
...What? I was just worried about you!
I can't even worry about you?

rows.label: qst700108_msg0008
rows.name:
No, you can do whatever you want, I...
I... I don't even know what to say...

rows.label: qst700108_msg0009
rows.name: ...Whatever! We're not talking about it!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0010
rows.name:
What's important is that our Armus
came back home! So, thanks!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0011
rows.name:
We can celebrate with a fish feast,
right?

rows.label: qst700108_msg0012
rows.name:
Yeah! ...But who said there's gonna
be enough for you?

rows.label: qst700108_msg0013
rows.name:
Ohhhh you...! Who'd even want to come
to your stupid party?! You're dumb and
I don't even like you, so there!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0014
rows.name: Wh-what did I say?!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0015
rows.name:
It seems our work here isn't quite
over yet...

rows.label: qst700108_msg0016
rows.name: What do you think, Hugo?

rows.label: qst700108_msg0017
rows.name: Hm? Oh, right. Uhh...

rows.label: qst700108_msg0018
rows.name: ...Frankly, I don't think it's our business.

rows.label: qst700108_msg0019
rows.name:
So long as they can keep living their
simple lives, laughing and fighting as
the occasion merits...

rows.label: qst700108_msg0020
rows.name:
... Oh. Well. I suppose that does
come down to us after all, doesn't it?

rows.label: qst700108_msg0021
rows.name: Perhaps so, Majesty, but still...

rows.label: qst700108_msg0022
rows.name:
We understand how you feel.
However, it may be best to not dwell
on that. It can only burden you.

rows.label: qst700108_msg0023
rows.name:
He's right, you know. You might wanna
try living without thinking, like our pal
Adel here.

rows.label: qst700108_msg0024
rows.name: Hahahah! Minochi you wound me!

rows.label: qst700108_msg0025
rows.name:
But Hugo, we're all on the same side.
We've got each other's backs now.
No harm in relaxing a bit, is there?

rows.label: qst700108_msg0026
rows.name: ...You never change, do you, Adel?

rows.label: qst700108_msg0027
rows.name: Neither do you, old friend.

rows.label: qst700108_msg0028
rows.name: Well, at least you got out of your head.

rows.label: qst700108_msg0029
rows.name:
Nobody can keep the weight of all of
Alst on their shoulders. Do us a favor
and remember that, at least.
